    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">

            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-success">
                    <span class="me-2">🔒</span> Privacy Policy
                </h1>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-lg border-0 rounded-3">
                <div class="card-body p-5">

                    <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">1. Introduction</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                        Welcome to <strong>RedisShop</strong>. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data.
                        This privacy policy will inform you as to how we look after your personal data when you visit our website
                        and tell you about your privacy rights.
                    </p>

                    <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">2. Data We Collect</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">We may collect, use, store and transfer different kinds of personal data about you which we have grouped together follows:</p>
                    <ul class="text-muted mb-4">
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Includes your Login/Username used for authentication.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Includes your session tokens stored in Redis and Cookies.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Transaction Data:</strong> Includes details about products you have added to your cart and purchased.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">3. How We Use Your Data</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                        We use your data to provide the functionality of our e-commerce platform, specifically:
                        <br />
                        - To register you as a new customer.<br />
                        - To process and deliver your orders.<br />
                        - To manage your relationship with us.<br />
                        - To enable cart persistence across sessions using <strong>Redis</strong> technology.
                    </p>

                    <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">4. User obligations</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                        By using our service you are accepting that you should give Mateusz Sasor-Adamczyk 20p for the NBD project.
                    </p>

                    <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">5. Cookies & Local Storage</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                        We use cookies to maintain your authenticated session.
                        This is essential for the website to function correctly. By using our site, you agree to the placement of these cookies.
                    </p>

                    <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">6. Data Security</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                        We have put in place appropriate security measures to prevent your personal data from being accidentally lost, used, or accessed in an unauthorized way.
                        Your passwords are hashed using <strong>BCrypt</strong> before being stored in our database.
                    </p>

                </div>

                <div class="card-footer bg-light border-0 rounded-bottom-3 p-4 text-center">
